@startuml
title Guide 4.2 - MovieService RMI Architecture

actor "User" as user
participant "MovieRmiClient" as client
participant "RMI Registry\n(:23000)" as registry
participant "MovieServiceImpl" as server
database "MovieRepository\n(in memory)" as repo

user -> client : types movie ID
client -> registry : lookup("movieService")
registry --> client : remote stub
client -> server : getMovie(1)\n(remote call)
server -> repo : findById(1)
repo --> server : Movie
server --> client : serialized Movie
client --> user : display result

legend right
  Contract: MovieService interface
  Java-only (RMI)
  Serializable required
endlegend

@enduml